sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser (SPA)
    participant Django as Django Backend
    participant DB as Django DB

    Browser->>Django: POST /api/auth/login/start/<br/>{"email":"user@example.com","password":"secret"}
    Django->>DB: authenticate(email, password)
    DB-->>Django: User object
    Django->>DB: _has_confirmed_otp_device(user) → false
    DB-->>Django: false
    Django-->>Browser: 200 OK<br/>{"mfa_required": false, "token": "abc123"}

    Note over Browser: Login complete — store token
